query.sfwSql: SELECT *,'' AS IS_RETIREE_HEALTH_ENROLLED,'' AS IS_PARTD_HEALTH_ENROLLED, IS_DB_PLAN_ENROLED AS IS_PLAN_DB ,IS_DC_PLAN_ENROLED AS IS_PLAN_DC,FULL_NAME AS PAYEE_NAME, C.ACCOUNT_RELATION_VALUE AS ACCOUNT_RELATIONSHIP_VALUE,CASE WHEN PL.PLAN_NAME IS NULL THEN '' ELSE PL.PLAN_NAME + ' Retirement' END AS PLAN_NAME, CV.DESCRIPTION AS ACCOUNT_RELATIONSHIP_DESC, CASE WHEN C.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE='DISA' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS IS_BENEFIT_TYPE_DISABILITY,MBR.STATEMENT_EFFECTIVE_DATE, ISNULL(M.FIRST_NAME,'') + ' ' + ISNULL(M.MIDDLE_NAME,'') + ' ' + ISNULL(M.LAST_NAME,'') AS OWNER_NAME , ISNULL(M.FIRST_NAME,'') AS OWNER_FIRST_NAME,CASE WHEN A.ADDR_STATE_DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL THEN (SELECT C.CODE_VALUE FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE C WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE CODE_ID=150 AND C.DESCRIPTION=ADDR_STATE_DESCRIPTION) END AS STATE_VALUE, CASE WHEN ADDR_COUNTRY_VALUE='0001' THEN '' ELSE ADDR_COUNTRY_DESCRIPTION END AS COUNTRY, CASE WHEN BRCMEMBER.RHIC_CREATED IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE CASE WHEN BRC1.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS not NULL Or BRC2.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS not NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END END AS IS_COMBINING_RHIC, ISNULL(BRCMEMBER.APPLY_TO_VALUE,'N') AS IS_RHIC_APPLIED_HEALTH, ISNULL(BENACCT.RHIC_BENEFIT_AMOUNT, 0.0) AS MEMBERRHICAMOUNT, --ISNULL(CASE WHEN BRCMEMBER.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN BRCMEMBER.RHICAMT --WHEN BRC2.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN BRC2.RHICAMT --WHEN BRC1.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN BRC1.RHICAMT --ELSE BRCMEMBER.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT END,0.0) AS MEMBERRHICAMOUNT, ISNULL(CASE WHEN BRCMEMBER.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN CASE WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE='RD50' THEN BRCMEMBER.RHICAMT/2 WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('R100','STRD') THEN BRCMEMBER.RHICAMT END WHEN BRC2.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN CASE WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE='RD50' THEN BRC2.RHICAMT/2 WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('R100','STRD') THEN BRC2.RHICAMT END WHEN BRC1.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN CASE WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE='RD50' THEN BRC1.RHICAMT/2 WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('R100','STRD') THEN BRC1.RHICAMT END ELSE CASE WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE='RD50' THEN BRCMEMBER.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT/2 WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('R100','STRD') THEN BRCMEMBER.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT END END,0.0) AS SPOUSERHICAMOUNT, --ISNULL(BENACCT.RHIC_BENEFIT_AMOUNT, 0.0) AS MEMBERRHICAMOUNT, --ISNULL(BENACCT.SPOUSE_RHIC_AMOUNT, 0.0) AS SPOUSERHICAMOUNT, '' AS DISPLAY_RHIC, '' AS HEALTH_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS VISION_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS DENTAL_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS LIFE_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS LTC_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS MEDICARE_PREMIUM_AMT FROM SGT_MAS_PERSON A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_SELECTION B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_SELECTION_ID=B.MAS_SELECTION_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_MAS_PAYEE_ACCOUNT C WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_PERSON_ID=C.MAS_PERSON_ID LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV WITH(NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID=C.ACCOUNT_RELATION_ID AND CV.CODE_VALUE=C.ACCOUNT_RELATION_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON M WITH(NOLOCK) ON M.PERSON_ID=C.MEMBER_PERSON_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PAYACCT WITH(NOLOCK) ON C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAYACCT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT BENACCT WITH(NOLOCK) ON PAYACCT.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = BENACCT.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_BATCH_REQUEST MBR WITH(NOLOCK) ON MBR.MAS_BATCH_REQUEST_ID=B.MAS_BATCH_REQUEST_ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT RHCOMB.PERSON_ID,RHCOMB.START_DATE,RHCOMB.END_DATE,RHCOMB.RHIC_CREATED,RHCOMB.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, CASE WHEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0)>0 THEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) ELSE DETL.RHIC_AMOUNT END AS RHICAMT,DETL.* FROM ( SELECT * FROM (SELECT BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID,PERSON_ID,START_DATE,END_DATE,CREATED_BY AS RHIC_CREATED, ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) AS COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY PERSON_ID ORDER BY ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') DESC,START_DATE DESC ,BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID DESC ) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE RC WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE @PAYMENTDATE BETWEEN RC.START_DATE AND (CASE WHEN RC.END_DATE IS NULL THEN '99991231' ELSE RC.END_DATE END) AND ACTION_STATUS_VALUE IN ( 'APPR','ENDD') --AND ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> ISNULL(TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) --and ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> 0 ) A WHERE A.ROWRANK = 1 ) RHCOMB LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL DETL WITH(NOLOCK) ON DETL.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID = RHCOMB.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT DPAC WITH(NOLOCK) ON DETL.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = DPAC.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE DPAC.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID <> RHCOMB.PERSON_ID ) AS BRC1 ON BRC1.PERSON_ID=B.PERSON_ID AND ISNULL(BRC1.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,0) <> C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT RHCOMB.PERSON_ID,RHCOMB.START_DATE,RHCOMB.END_DATE,RHCOMB.RHIC_CREATED,RHCOMB.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, CASE WHEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0)>0 THEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) ELSE DETL.RHIC_AMOUNT END AS RHICAMT,APPLY_TO_VALUE,DETL.* FROM ( SELECT * FROM (SELECT BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID,PERSON_ID,START_DATE,END_DATE,CREATED_BY AS RHIC_CREATED,APPLY_TO_VALUE, ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) AS COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY PERSON_ID ORDER BY ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') DESC,START_DATE DESC ,BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID DESC ) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE RC WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE @PAYMENTDATE BETWEEN RC.START_DATE AND (CASE WHEN RC.END_DATE IS NULL THEN '99991231' ELSE RC.END_DATE END) AND ACTION_STATUS_VALUE IN ( 'APPR','ENDD') --AND ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> ISNULL(TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) --and ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> 0 ) A WHERE A.ROWRANK = 1 ) RHCOMB INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL DETL WITH(NOLOCK) ON DETL.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID = RHCOMB.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID ) BRCMEMBER ON BRCMEMBER.PERSON_ID=C.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID AND ISNULL(BRCMEMBER.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID) = C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT RHCOMB.PERSON_ID,RHCOMB.START_DATE,RHCOMB.END_DATE,RHCOMB.RHIC_CREATED,RHCOMB.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, CASE WHEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0)>0 THEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) ELSE DETL.RHIC_AMOUNT END AS RHICAMT,DETL.* FROM (SELECT * FROM (SELECT BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID,PERSON_ID,START_DATE,END_DATE,CREATED_BY AS RHIC_CREATED, ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) AS COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY PERSON_ID ORDER BY ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') DESC,START_DATE DESC ,BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID DESC ) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE RC WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE @PAYMENTDATE BETWEEN RC.START_DATE AND (CASE WHEN RC.END_DATE IS NULL THEN '99991231' ELSE RC.END_DATE END) AND ACTION_STATUS_VALUE IN ( 'APPR','ENDD') --AND ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> ISNULL(TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) --and ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> 0 ) A WHERE A.ROWRANK = 1 ) RHCOMB LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL DETL WITH(NOLOCK) ON DETL.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID = RHCOMB.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID ) BRC2 ON BRC2.PERSON_ID<>C.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID AND ISNULL(BRC2.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,0) = C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PLAN PL WITH(NOLOCK) ON PL.PLAN_ID=C.PLAN_ID WHERE MBR.MAS_BATCH_REQUEST_ID=@BATCHREQUESTID

SELECT *,'' AS IS_RETIREE_HEALTH_ENROLLED,'' AS IS_PARTD_HEALTH_ENROLLED, IS_DB_PLAN_ENROLED AS IS_PLAN_DB ,IS_DC_PLAN_ENROLED AS IS_PLAN_DC,FULL_NAME AS PAYEE_NAME, C.ACCOUNT_RELATION_VALUE AS ACCOUNT_RELATIONSHIP_VALUE,PL.PLAN_NAME + ' Retirement' AS PLAN_NAME, CV.DESCRIPTION AS ACCOUNT_RELATIONSHIP_DESC, CASE WHEN C.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE='DISA' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS IS_BENEFIT_TYPE_DISABILITY,MBR.STATEMENT_EFFECTIVE_DATE, ISNULL(M.FIRST_NAME,'') + ' ' + ISNULL(M.MIDDLE_NAME,'') + ' ' + ISNULL(M.LAST_NAME,'') AS OWNER_NAME , ISNULL(M.FIRST_NAME,'') AS OWNER_FIRST_NAME,CASE WHEN A.ADDR_STATE_DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL THEN (SELECT C.CODE_VALUE FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE C WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE CODE_ID=150 AND C.DESCRIPTION=ADDR_STATE_DESCRIPTION) END AS STATE_VALUE, CASE WHEN ADDR_COUNTRY_VALUE='0001' THEN '' ELSE ADDR_COUNTRY_DESCRIPTION END AS COUNTRY, CASE WHEN BRCMEMBER.RHIC_CREATED IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE CASE WHEN BRC1.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS not NULL Or BRC2.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS not NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END END AS IS_COMBINING_RHIC, ISNULL(BRCMEMBER.APPLY_TO_VALUE,'N') AS IS_RHIC_APPLIED_HEALTH, --pir 8650 ISNULL(BENACCT.RHIC_BENEFIT_AMOUNT, 0.0) AS MEMBERRHICAMOUNT, --ISNULL(CASE WHEN BRCMEMBER.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN BRCMEMBER.RHICAMT --WHEN BRC2.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN BRC2.RHICAMT --WHEN BRC1.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN BRC1.RHICAMT --ELSE BRCMEMBER.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT END,0.0) AS MEMBERRHICAMOUNT, ISNULL(CASE WHEN BRCMEMBER.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN CASE WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE='RD50' THEN BRCMEMBER.RHICAMT/2 WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('R100','STRD') THEN BRCMEMBER.RHICAMT END WHEN BRC2.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN CASE WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE='RD50' THEN BRC2.RHICAMT/2 WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('R100','STRD') THEN BRC2.RHICAMT END WHEN BRC1.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN CASE WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE='RD50' THEN BRC1.RHICAMT/2 WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('R100','STRD') THEN BRC1.RHICAMT END ELSE CASE WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE='RD50' THEN BRCMEMBER.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT/2 WHEN C.RHIC_BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('R100','STRD') THEN BRCMEMBER.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT END END,0.0) AS SPOUSERHICAMOUNT, --ISNULL(BENACCT.RHIC_BENEFIT_AMOUNT, 0.0) AS MEMBERRHICAMOUNT, --ISNULL(BENACCT.SPOUSE_RHIC_AMOUNT, 0.0) AS SPOUSERHICAMOUNT, '' AS DISPLAY_RHIC, '' AS HEALTH_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS VISION_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS DENTAL_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS LIFE_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS LTC_PREMIUM_AMT, '' AS MEDICARE_PREMIUM_AMT FROM SGT_MAS_PERSON A INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_SELECTION B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_SELECTION_ID=B.MAS_SELECTION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_BATCH_REQUEST MBR WITH(NOLOCK) ON MBR.MAS_BATCH_REQUEST_ID=B.MAS_BATCH_REQUEST_ID LEFT JOIN DBO.SGT_MAS_PAYEE_ACCOUNT C WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_PERSON_ID=C.MAS_PERSON_ID LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV WITH(NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID=C.ACCOUNT_RELATION_ID AND CV.CODE_VALUE=C.ACCOUNT_RELATION_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON M WITH(NOLOCK) ON M.PERSON_ID=C.MEMBER_PERSON_ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT RHCOMB.PERSON_ID,RHCOMB.START_DATE,RHCOMB.END_DATE,RHCOMB.RHIC_CREATED,RHCOMB.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, CASE WHEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0)>0 THEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) ELSE DETL.RHIC_AMOUNT END AS RHICAMT,DETL.* FROM ( SELECT * FROM (SELECT BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID,PERSON_ID,START_DATE,END_DATE,CREATED_BY AS RHIC_CREATED, ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) AS COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY PERSON_ID ORDER BY ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') DESC,START_DATE DESC ,BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID DESC ) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE RC WHERE @PAYMENTDATE BETWEEN RC.START_DATE AND (CASE WHEN RC.END_DATE IS NULL THEN '99991231' ELSE RC.END_DATE END) AND ACTION_STATUS_VALUE IN ( 'APPR','ENDD') --AND ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> ISNULL(TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) --and ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> 0 ) A WHERE A.ROWRANK = 1 ) RHCOMB LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL DETL ON DETL.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID = RHCOMB.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT DPAC ON DETL.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = DPAC.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE DPAC.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID <> RHCOMB.PERSON_ID ) AS BRC1 ON BRC1.PERSON_ID=B.PERSON_ID AND ISNULL(BRC1.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,0) <> C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT RHCOMB.PERSON_ID,RHCOMB.START_DATE,RHCOMB.END_DATE,RHCOMB.RHIC_CREATED,RHCOMB.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, CASE WHEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0)>0 THEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) ELSE DETL.RHIC_AMOUNT END AS RHICAMT,APPLY_TO_VALUE,DETL.* FROM ( SELECT * FROM (SELECT BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID,PERSON_ID,START_DATE,END_DATE,CREATED_BY AS RHIC_CREATED,APPLY_TO_VALUE, ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) AS COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY PERSON_ID ORDER BY ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') DESC,START_DATE DESC ,BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID DESC ) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE RC WHERE @PAYMENTDATE BETWEEN RC.START_DATE AND (CASE WHEN RC.END_DATE IS NULL THEN '99991231' ELSE RC.END_DATE END) AND ACTION_STATUS_VALUE IN ( 'APPR','ENDD') --AND ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> ISNULL(TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) --and ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> 0 ) A WHERE A.ROWRANK = 1 ) RHCOMB INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL DETL ON DETL.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID = RHCOMB.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID ) BRCMEMBER ON BRCMEMBER.PERSON_ID=C.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID AND ISNULL(BRCMEMBER.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID) = C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT RHCOMB.PERSON_ID,RHCOMB.START_DATE,RHCOMB.END_DATE,RHCOMB.RHIC_CREATED,RHCOMB.COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, CASE WHEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0)>0 THEN ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) + ISNULL(RHCOMB.TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) ELSE DETL.RHIC_AMOUNT END AS RHICAMT,DETL.* FROM (SELECT * FROM (SELECT BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID,PERSON_ID,START_DATE,END_DATE,CREATED_BY AS RHIC_CREATED, ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) AS COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT, TOTAL_OTHER_RHIC_AMOUNT,TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY PERSON_ID ORDER BY ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') DESC,START_DATE DESC ,BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID DESC ) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE RC WHERE @PAYMENTDATE BETWEEN RC.START_DATE AND (CASE WHEN RC.END_DATE IS NULL THEN '99991231' ELSE RC.END_DATE END) AND ACTION_STATUS_VALUE IN ( 'APPR','ENDD') --AND ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> ISNULL(TOTAL_JS_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) --and ISNULL(COMBINED_RHIC_AMOUNT,0) <> 0 ) A WHERE A.ROWRANK = 1 ) RHCOMB LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL DETL ON DETL.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID = RHCOMB.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID ) BRC2 ON BRC2.PERSON_ID<>C.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID AND ISNULL(BRC2.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,0) = C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID left JOIN SGT_PLAN PL ON PL.PLAN_ID=C.PLAN_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_MAS_PAYEE_ACCOUNT MP ON A.MAS_PERSON_ID=MP.MAS_PERSON_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PAYACCT ON MP.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAYACCT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT BENACCT ON PAYACCT.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = BENACCT.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID --PIR 8650 --LEFT JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_DETAIL BRCD1 -- ON BRC.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID=BRCD1.BENEFIT_RHIC_COMBINE_ID and BRCD1.DONAR_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID=C.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID where b.MAS_SELECTION_ID=@MAS_SELECTION_ID

SELECT A.MAS_SELECTION_ID AS MAS_SELECTION_ID, 'IS_HEALTH_ENROLLED' AS PLAN_NAME, IS_HEALTH_ENROLLED AS PLAN_NAME_VALUE, B.PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_MAS_PERSON A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_SELECTION B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_SELECTION_ID=B.MAS_SELECTION_ID WHERE A.MAS_SELECTION_ID = @MAS_SELECTION_ID AND IS_HEALTH_ENROLLED = 'Y' UNION ALL SELECT A.MAS_SELECTION_ID AS MAS_SELECTION_ID, 'IS_LIFE_ENROLLED' AS PLAN_NAME, IS_LIFE_ENROLLED AS PLAN_NAME_VALUE, B.PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_MAS_PERSON A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_SELECTION B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_SELECTION_ID=B.MAS_SELECTION_ID WHERE A.MAS_SELECTION_ID = @MAS_SELECTION_ID AND IS_LIFE_ENROLLED = 'Y' UNION ALL SELECT A.MAS_SELECTION_ID AS MAS_SELECTION_ID, 'IS_LTC_ENROLLED' AS PLAN_NAME, IS_LTC_ENROLLED AS PLAN_NAME_VALUE, B.PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_MAS_PERSON A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_SELECTION B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_SELECTION_ID=B.MAS_SELECTION_ID WHERE A.MAS_SELECTION_ID = @MAS_SELECTION_ID AND IS_LTC_ENROLLED = 'Y' UNION ALL SELECT A.MAS_SELECTION_ID AS MAS_SELECTION_ID, 'IS_VISION_ENROLLED' AS PLAN_NAME, IS_VISION_ENROLLED AS PLAN_NAME_VALUE, B.PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_MAS_PERSON A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_SELECTION B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_SELECTION_ID=B.MAS_SELECTION_ID WHERE A.MAS_SELECTION_ID = @MAS_SELECTION_ID AND IS_VISION_ENROLLED = 'Y' UNION ALL SELECT A.MAS_SELECTION_ID AS MAS_SELECTION_ID, 'IS_DENTAL_ENROLLED' AS PLAN_NAME, IS_DENTAL_ENROLLED AS PLAN_NAME_VALUE, B.PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_MAS_PERSON A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_MAS_SELECTION B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.MAS_SELECTION_ID=B.MAS_SELECTION_ID WHERE A.MAS_SELECTION_ID = @MAS_SELECTION_ID AND IS_DENTAL_ENROLLED = 'Y'

SELECT ISNULL(SUM(ISNULL(ALLOCATED_AMOUNT,0.00)), 0.00) AS PAID_PREMIUM_AMOUNT FROM SGT_IBS_REMITTANCE_ALLOCATION WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = @PERSONACCOUNTID AND YEAR(EFFECTIVE_DATE) = @EFFECTIVEYEAR

SELECT ISNULL(SUM(PAID_PREMIUM_AMOUNT),0.00) as PAID_PREMIUM_AMOUNT FROM DBO.SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_INSURANCE_CONTRIBUTION WHERE YEAR(EFFECTIVE_DATE) =@EFFECTIVEYEAR AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = @PERSONACCOUNTID

SELECT ISNULL(SUM(ISNULL(CONT.ALLOCATED_AMOUNT,0.00)), 0.00) AS PAID_PREMIUM_AMOUNT FROM DBO.SGT_IBS_REMITTANCE_ALLOCATION CONT WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_MEDICARE_PART_D_HISTORY MED WITH(NOLOCK) ON MED.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = CONT.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE YEAR(CONT.EFFECTIVE_DATE) =@EFFECTIVEYEAR AND MED.END_DATE IS NULL AND MED.MEMBER_PERSON_ID = @MEMBERPERSONID
